@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### Publish a text message (preferred endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kafka/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello from the HTTP client"
}

### Publish a user message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kafka/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "firstName": "Mohamed",
  "lastName": "Tamer"
}

### Legacy text endpoint (kept for backward compatibility)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kafka/publish?message=Hello%20from%20the%20legacy%20endpoint

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### Invalid user (returns HTTP 400 Problem Details)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/kafka/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "Tamer"
}
